        <h2>Tiramisu</h2>
        <img src="http://www.roadtopastry.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/Recipe-Traditional-Tiramisu-01.jpg alt="Image of the Italian 
        coffee-flavored dessert" title="Italian dessert Tiramisu" height="200">
        
        <p>Ingredients for 4 persons (or one person very greedy like me)</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>6</b> eggs</li>
          <li><b>1</b> package of Savoiardi biscuits</li>
          <li><b>1</b> cup of Italian coffee</li>
          <li><b>120</b>g sugar plus 2 little spoon for the coffee</li>
          <li><b>500</b>g of mascarpone cheese</li>
          <li>cocoa powder</li>
        </ul>
    <br />
