     <article id="pizza">
        <h2>Pizza</h2>
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/Eq_it-na_pizza-margherita_sep2005_sml.jpg/390px-Eq_it-na_pizza-
        margherita_sep2005_sml.jpg" alt="Image of the Margherita pizza" title="Margherita pizza" height="200">
        
        <p>Ingredients for 4 persons</p>
        <p>For the base</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>1</b>k strong bread flour</li>
          <li><b>600</b>g water</li>
          <li><b>60</b>g extra virgin olive oil plus extra for drizzling</li>
          <li><b>20</b>g salt</li>
          <li><b>7</b>g baker's yeast</li>
          <li><b>2</b> little spoons of sugar</li>
        </ul>
         <p>For the tomato sauce</p>
          <ul>
          <li><b>500</b>ml passata</li>
          <li>b>handful fresh basil</li>
          <li>extra virgin olive oil, to taste
        </ul>
        <p>For the topping</p>
         <ul>
          <li><b>500</b>g ball mozzarella, sliced</li>
          <li>b>handful basil leaves</li>
        </ul>
    <br />
        <p>Directions</p>
          <ul>
            <li><b>Step 1</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 2</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 3</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 4</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 5</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
         </ul>
    </article>
    
     <article id="linguine">
        <h2>Linguine with pesto</h2>
        <img src="http://cdn.gingerandtomato.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Spaghetti-al-pesto-di-pistacchi-e-mandorle.jpg" 
        alt="Image of linguine with Italian sauce  pesto" title="Italian dessert Tiramisu" height="200">
        
        <p>Ingredients (serves 4 or 6)</p>
        <p>For the pesto</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>2</b> cups fresh basil leaves</li>
          <li><b>3</b> tbsp of pine nuts, toasted</li>
          <li><b>2</b> small cloves of garlic</li>
          <li>&frac12; cup extra virgin olive oil</li> 
          <li>&frac12; cup of fresh Parmiggiano Reggiano</li>
          <li>salt and pepper, to taste</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For the remaining ingredients</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>1</b>k of linguine</li> 
          <li>salt and pepper</li>
          <li>freshly grated Parmiggiano Reggiano</li>
    <br />
        <p>Process</p>
          <ul>
            <li><b>Step 1</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 2</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 3</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 4</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
            <li><b>Step 5</b> - Bla, bla, bla ... </li>
         </ul>
